{"pageProps":{"article":{"id":"b489fa71e5","title":"刘涛揭发的王光美与刘少奇的讲话","origin":"","is_range_date":false,"dates":[{"id":"b0f71427d1","index":0,"year":1966,"month":7,"day":3,"articleId":"b489fa71e5"}],"tags":[{"id":"1f0a0507bf","name":"王光美","type":"人物"},{"id":"3aaab89c2a","name":"刘少奇","type":"人物"},{"id":"8120da8484","name":"刘涛","type":"人物"},{"id":"e23dcf99fa","name":"发言","type":"文稿类型"}],"aliases":[],"publications":[{"id":"GPCRv3","name":"中国文化大革命文库（第三版）","internal":true,"official":false,"type":"db","author":"宋永毅","files":""}],"authors":[{"id":"84ad624f40","name":"王光美"},{"id":"9986567b57","name":"刘少奇"},{"id":"ae8a93a2cb","name":"刘涛"}]},"publication_details":{"GPCRv3":{"comments":[],"contents":[{"id":"40c0e0d56e","type":"title","text":"刘涛揭发的王光美与刘少奇的讲话","index":0,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"b489fa71e5"},{"id":"e91c0181b3","type":"authors","text":"刘涛王光美刘少奇","index":1,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"b489fa71e5"},{"id":"487262453e","type":"paragraph","text":"（刘涛揭发：）在七月三日晚上我记得她（王光美）跟我讲过一次话……记得有这么几点：","index":2,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"b489fa71e5"},{"id":"182b271f65","type":"paragraph","text":"一、要把蒯大富当活靶子打。","index":3,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"b489fa71e5"},{"id":"7a1cf6d6c0","type":"paragraph","text":"二、要把蒯大富他们一派搞成少数，批倒了他们才能巩固工作组的地位。三、资产阶级不给我们民主，我们也不给他们民主。","index":4,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"b489fa71e5"},{"id":"13a666d9e2","type":"paragraph","text":"七月二十八日，刘少奇异常激动地对我和王光美说：","index":5,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"b489fa71e5"},{"id":"11c6eb7372","type":"paragraph","text":"一、现在不是要检讨吗？要我到你们学校去检讨也可以，去就去，没有什么可怕的。","index":6,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"b489fa71e5"},{"id":"0be223fd96","type":"paragraph","text":"二、工作组的工作是当着大家的面做的。（意思就是说，是好是坏，大家都能检验出来。）","index":7,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"b489fa71e5"},{"id":"d1ffcf82a4","type":"paragraph","text":"三、工作组现在也没有什么事情了，你们就劳动，帮助抄大字报，扫扫地，这样别的同学也就不会说你们当官做老爷了。四、蒯大富是自己跳出来的，而不是工作组把他打成反革命的。","index":8,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"b489fa71e5"}],"page":{"id":"8ee40c6ada","publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"b489fa71e5","start":0,"end":0}}}},"__N_SSG":true}